title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jun 8 2022

description:
What we've learned about would-be Kavanaugh killer Nicholas John Roske. Matthew McConaughey pushing Democrat gun control myths. Former Nevada AG Adam Laxalt joins Clay and Buck to discuss the attempt on Justice Kavanaugh's life, the Uvalde shooting and the dangerous threats we face from the left. C&B take calls to end the show.
